1
00:01:11,680 --> 00:01:12,760
Rock, paper, scissors.

2
00:01:12,760 --> 00:01:13,680
Sweetie.

3
00:01:13,680 --> 00:01:14,680
Go to sleep now.

4
00:01:14,680 --> 00:01:15,520
Go to sleep.

5
00:01:15,880 --> 00:01:17,240
Come here, Xiao Hua.

6
00:01:17,240 --> 00:01:18,600
Go to sleep.

7
00:01:20,880 --> 00:01:23,520
Big sister, are you here to take me home?

8
00:01:36,640 --> 00:01:38,080
I've packed enough things.

9
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,240
Stop worrying about it.

10
00:01:39,320 --> 00:01:40,120
No way.

11
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:41,120
You have never...

12
00:01:41,120 --> 00:01:42,560
...gone on such a long trip before.

13
00:01:42,760 --> 00:01:44,080
How can I not worry?

14
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:47,720
Here.

15
00:01:49,320 --> 00:01:50,960
Then remember to come to Tuo Cheng to pick me up.

16
00:01:53,960 --> 00:01:55,160
I definitely will.

17
00:02:01,880 --> 00:02:03,680
Pack me up and take me with you, sis.

18
00:02:04,440 --> 00:02:05,440
Stop it.

19
00:02:19,000 --> 00:02:19,600
Sweetie.

20
00:02:19,880 --> 00:02:21,640
Let's go to sleep.

21
00:02:21,640 --> 00:02:22,640
Go to sleep.

22
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:29,600
I'll take you there.

23
00:02:30,600 --> 00:02:31,200
Let's go.

24
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:36,160
Come on.

25
00:02:42,080 --> 00:02:42,920
Over here.

26
00:02:43,880 --> 00:02:44,840
It's just ahead.

27
00:02:46,960 --> 00:02:47,800
A Dong.

28
00:02:59,080 --> 00:03:00,000
Director.

29
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:03,800
Is... is Mom here to pick me up?

30
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:24,240
On here...

31
00:03:24,400 --> 00:03:26,160
...draw a few apples.

32
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,720
One apple.

33
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:30,320
Two apples.

34
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:32,440
Three apples.

35
00:03:32,680 --> 00:03:34,600
This biggest apple is for A Dong.

36
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:36,200
Do you like apples?

37
00:03:38,560 --> 00:03:40,320
Draw a big apple.

38
00:03:40,640 --> 00:03:41,760
Great job.

39
00:03:42,880 --> 00:03:43,680
Jiang Li.

40
00:03:49,920 --> 00:03:51,160
Big Sister Shen Man.

41
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,480
Big Sister Jiang Li.

42
00:03:52,720 --> 00:03:54,840
Will you come to see me again?

43
00:03:58,320 --> 00:03:59,320
We will.

44
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:02,720
Pinky promise.

45
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:05,040
Pinky swear...

46
00:04:05,040 --> 00:04:07,160
...forever and ever.

47
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,520
Stamped.

48
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,880
His eyes...

49
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:29,880
When he was brought here...

50
00:04:29,880 --> 00:04:31,920
...were already almost blind.

51
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:33,760
He had injuries on his body too.

52
00:04:34,400 --> 00:04:35,440
He's still so young.

53
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,440
To have gone through so much.

54
00:04:38,320 --> 00:04:39,440
Then his eyes...

55
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:40,880
...can they still recover?

56
00:04:41,400 --> 00:04:42,400
The doctor said...

57
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:44,000
...as long as he has surgery soon...

58
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:46,560
...there's still hope to restore his vision.

59
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:50,000
It's just the surgery fee...

60
00:04:50,880 --> 00:04:51,920
I'll figure something out.

61
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:56,200
Thank you so much.

62
00:04:56,480 --> 00:04:58,120
I thank you on A Dong's behalf.

63
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:00,600
You're welcome.

64
00:05:04,160 --> 00:05:05,040
This box...

65
00:05:05,760 --> 00:05:07,200
...was with A Dong's...

66
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:08,320
...belongings.

67
00:05:09,160 --> 00:05:11,600
I don't know if it'll help the case.

68
00:05:12,760 --> 00:05:14,000
I'll leave it to you.

69
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:19,000
Thank you.

70
00:05:35,560 --> 00:05:37,800
Only this last room is left.

71
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,800
It's a letter from Lisa to A Dong.

72
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:47,120
It's a pity A Dong can't see anymore.

73
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,760
I'll post these...

74
00:05:50,760 --> 00:05:51,840
...on our account right now.

75
00:05:52,040 --> 00:05:53,600
There must be a professional ophthalmologist...

76
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:54,960
...who will see this and contact us.

77
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,240
Okay.

78
00:05:58,680 --> 00:06:00,000
A Dong will definitely see...

79
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:00,840
...this letter with his own eyes.

80
00:06:03,120 --> 00:06:04,240
He definitely will.

81
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:25,880
There seems to be writing on this drawing.

82
00:06:26,920 --> 00:06:27,680
Look.

83
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,000
There's writing on every page.

84
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,120
It looks like Lisa's diary.

85
00:06:47,120 --> 00:06:48,520
February 3rd.

86
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:50,880
This is the 100th day of our love.

87
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:08,120
March 15th, the first time he met my parents.

88
00:07:08,120 --> 00:07:09,640
I will definitely treat Lisa well.

89
00:07:10,240 --> 00:07:10,920
Dad.

90
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:14,240
What are you doing, Dad?

91
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:22,400
I'm sorry.

92
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:23,240
It's all my fault.

93
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,440
Trust me.

94
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:25,680
I'll convince my dad.

95
00:07:29,560 --> 00:07:30,360
Thank you.

96
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:37,480
Mother passed away.

97
00:07:37,480 --> 00:07:39,440
I spent a long time recovering from a car accident.

98
00:07:45,000 --> 00:07:47,000
Ah Hui knew I loved eating fish.

99
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:48,600
I thought it was always him...

100
00:07:48,600 --> 00:07:50,680
...who carefully picked out the fish bones for me.

101
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:52,960
But I didn't know...

102
00:07:53,560 --> 00:07:55,480
...that it was Father doing it for me all along.

103
00:08:25,480 --> 00:08:26,360
Why are you here?

104
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:27,120
Get out.

105
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:29,120
My brother gave those two old geezers' house...

106
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:30,120
...to me to live in.

107
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:32,040
Hurry up and give me the keys.

108
00:08:46,440 --> 00:08:47,360
Father passed away.

109
00:08:48,240 --> 00:08:49,600
Home is no longer a synonym...

110
00:08:49,600 --> 00:08:51,200
...for warmth and happiness.

111
00:08:52,560 --> 00:08:54,400
This place that was full of love...

112
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:56,280
...now feels like hell.

113
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,960
Maybe it's not that Ah Hui changed.

114
00:08:59,440 --> 00:09:00,840
It's that I see him clearly now.

115
00:09:02,040 --> 00:09:03,960
I know what awaits me.

116
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,680
For A Dong's sake...

117
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,640
...I have to prepare early.

118
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:29,440
Lose again, drink again!

119
00:09:35,800 --> 00:09:37,040
Where are you going this late?

120
00:09:39,360 --> 00:09:40,240
True.

121
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:42,680
After all, a rich family's daughter...

122
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:45,320
...it's normal she looks down on us.

123
00:09:48,760 --> 00:09:49,440
In a bit...

124
00:09:50,560 --> 00:09:53,120
...I want you to kneel and serve us.

125
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:55,680
Go.

126
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:56,680
Go.

127
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:08,000
Okay.

128
00:10:13,680 --> 00:10:14,560
You think the booze is free?

129
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:17,680
You think the booze is free?

130
00:10:21,800 --> 00:10:22,800
What are you afraid of?

131
00:10:23,920 --> 00:10:24,920
What are you afraid of?

132
00:10:25,560 --> 00:10:26,680
What are you afraid of?

133
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:37,280
Lick it clean.

134
00:10:42,560 --> 00:10:44,320
I told you to lick it clean!

135
00:11:03,520 --> 00:11:05,560
Open up. Open up. Open up.

136
00:11:08,680 --> 00:11:09,440
That's right.

137
00:11:16,800 --> 00:11:18,320
Stick out your tongue.

138
00:11:29,960 --> 00:11:31,520
Lick it all clean.

139
00:11:57,680 --> 00:11:59,040
Lick it!

140
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:01,120
Lick!

141
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:12,520
So A Dong's eyes...

142
00:12:13,440 --> 00:12:15,320
...went blind because of this.

143
00:12:26,680 --> 00:12:27,320
Sister Shen Man.

144
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,560
A doctor contacted us saying...

145
00:12:29,560 --> 00:12:31,400
...he is willing to help treat A Dong's eyes.

146
00:12:32,800 --> 00:12:33,640
That's great.

147
00:12:34,560 --> 00:12:36,000
A Dong's eyes can be saved.

148
00:12:41,480 --> 00:12:43,360
Netizens are all condemning Cheng Hui.

149
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:45,400
For killing Lisa's family for money.

150
00:12:45,840 --> 00:12:46,720
They feel that...

151
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:49,080
...the killer punished Cheng Hui.

152
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:50,680
They treat him as a hero.

153
00:12:51,080 --> 00:12:53,960
They even gave him a name: The Arbiter.

154
00:12:56,360 --> 00:12:57,600
The Arbiter.

155
00:12:58,840 --> 00:13:00,240
Maybe life...

156
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:02,040
...is naturally full of disappointments.

157
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:04,000
And a lot of unfairness.

158
00:13:05,520 --> 00:13:07,880
So people need spiritual comfort.

159
00:13:08,080 --> 00:13:09,440
Fighting evil with evil...

160
00:13:10,400 --> 00:13:12,200
...is considered a way, I guess.

161
00:13:12,520 --> 00:13:14,160
That may be true...

162
00:13:15,560 --> 00:13:16,920
...but now too many people...

163
00:13:16,920 --> 00:13:17,920
...are praising him.

164
00:13:19,080 --> 00:13:20,600
The fear is that there will be...

165
00:13:20,600 --> 00:13:22,040
...more people imitating him.

166
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:24,960
If everyone uses...

167
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:25,960
...uses this kind of method...

168
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,840
...to uphold the justice in their hearts...

169
00:13:28,160 --> 00:13:29,680
...wouldn't that be chaos?

170
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:39,440
What is justice, anyway?

171
00:13:41,680 --> 00:13:43,160
While following the case recently,

172
00:13:44,320 --> 00:13:45,680
I saw Anna,

173
00:13:46,040 --> 00:13:46,840
Lisa,

174
00:13:47,160 --> 00:13:47,960
Su Nian.

175
00:13:50,800 --> 00:13:52,560
When they faced darkness...

176
00:13:52,560 --> 00:13:53,800
...they resisted in pain.

177
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:56,840
Was that wrong too?

178
00:13:59,960 --> 00:14:01,560
If your sister's death...

179
00:14:01,960 --> 00:14:04,000
...is really as you guessed...

180
00:14:06,560 --> 00:14:07,560
...what will you do?

181
00:14:20,960 --> 00:14:21,960
I don't know.

182
00:14:26,760 --> 00:14:29,680
The justice I understand might be...

183
00:14:31,520 --> 00:14:33,680
seeing Anna Lisa's plight,

184
00:14:34,680 --> 00:14:36,520
and unable to stop clenching my fists,

185
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:39,680
but having to use even more strength

186
00:14:40,160 --> 00:14:41,840
to hold onto the rationality of the handcuffs.

187
00:14:43,320 --> 00:14:44,960
Perhaps they had no choice.

188
00:14:46,280 --> 00:14:48,520
I also want to heal the wounds in their hearts.

189
00:14:49,920 --> 00:14:50,800
But I will not erase

190
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:52,160
the evidence of their crimes.

191
00:15:15,680 --> 00:15:16,960
Shen Man, Jiang Li.

192
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:18,760
You're finally here. You're here.

193
00:15:19,480 --> 00:15:20,560
Sit, sit, sit.

194
00:15:20,880 --> 00:15:21,480
Okay.

195
00:15:21,480 --> 00:15:22,200
Sit.

196
00:15:28,560 --> 00:15:30,160
Did you miss us?

197
00:15:30,160 --> 00:15:31,200
Yes, I did.

198
00:15:33,560 --> 00:15:34,480
How is he doing?

199
00:15:34,640 --> 00:15:36,520
The surgery was very successful.

200
00:15:36,880 --> 00:15:38,000
The doctor said

201
00:15:38,000 --> 00:15:40,520
he can be discharged after a few days of recovery.

202
00:15:41,640 --> 00:15:42,480
That's great.

203
00:15:43,240 --> 00:15:44,520
Thanks to you guys

204
00:15:44,520 --> 00:15:46,520
posting that video online.

205
00:15:47,040 --> 00:15:47,880
The hospital

206
00:15:47,880 --> 00:15:49,920
waived most of the fees

207
00:15:50,080 --> 00:15:52,040
and scheduled the surgery early.

208
00:15:52,560 --> 00:15:56,480
I'm thanking you on behalf of A Dong.

209
00:15:56,920 --> 00:15:57,840
You're welcome.

210
00:15:58,560 --> 00:16:00,160
Seeing A Dong get better

211
00:16:00,440 --> 00:16:01,840
makes us happy too.

212
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:05,200
A Dong,

213
00:16:06,680 --> 00:16:09,720
this is a letter your mother wrote for you.

214
00:16:15,160 --> 00:16:16,280
A Dong.

215
00:16:16,440 --> 00:16:17,680
As a mother,

216
00:16:17,680 --> 00:16:19,200
I did a terrible job.

217
00:16:19,680 --> 00:16:21,440
I let you get hurt so much.

218
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:24,840
You used to ask me often

219
00:16:24,960 --> 00:16:26,920
why I always pinky promised with you.

220
00:16:27,840 --> 00:16:29,280
I'll tell you now.

221
00:16:30,560 --> 00:16:33,480
Every time we pinky promised, I said in my heart,

222
00:16:34,440 --> 00:16:36,280
the person I love most in this world

223
00:16:36,280 --> 00:16:37,600
is you.

224
00:16:38,320 --> 00:16:42,840
Pinky swear, unchanged for a hundred years.

225
00:16:42,840 --> 00:16:44,320
Seal it. Liars are puppies.

226
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:45,880
Seal it.

227
00:16:45,880 --> 00:16:46,920
A Dong.

228
00:16:47,320 --> 00:16:49,880
Unchanged for a hundred years.

229
00:16:51,400 --> 00:16:52,760
Regardless of whether

230
00:16:53,040 --> 00:16:54,880
you can see this letter in the end,

231
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:57,440
Mom knows

232
00:16:58,440 --> 00:16:59,640
that your eyes

233
00:17:00,440 --> 00:17:02,000
will definitely heal.

234
00:17:18,560 --> 00:17:20,640
We've checked Cheng Hui's social connections.

235
00:17:20,640 --> 00:17:21,560
There are no issues.

236
00:17:21,920 --> 00:17:22,800
After he got married,

237
00:17:22,800 --> 00:17:24,360
he lost touch with friends back home.

238
00:17:24,360 --> 00:17:26,080
He didn't have many friends in Tuo Cheng either.

239
00:17:28,320 --> 00:17:30,120
We also screened the gamblers.

240
00:17:30,480 --> 00:17:31,960
No... no leads.

241
00:17:33,000 --> 00:17:34,840
What about the pattern found at the scene?

242
00:17:34,840 --> 00:17:35,800
Did you find anything?

243
00:17:36,920 --> 00:17:38,240
The pattern is irregular.

244
00:17:38,640 --> 00:17:40,440
Technical analysis couldn't process it either.

245
00:17:40,560 --> 00:17:42,320
With just these two fragments,

246
00:17:42,320 --> 00:17:43,800
we haven't found any leads.

247
00:17:45,680 --> 00:17:47,280
No leads, no leads.

248
00:17:47,280 --> 00:17:49,280
You've been investigating for so long.

249
00:17:49,280 --> 00:17:51,160
Is "no leads" all you can say?

250
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:57,800
Chief.

251
00:17:59,040 --> 00:18:00,400
Although these two cases

252
00:18:00,400 --> 00:18:02,120
have been merged for investigation,

253
00:18:03,080 --> 00:18:04,280
the victims

254
00:18:04,560 --> 00:18:06,160
really don't have any connection.

255
00:18:06,320 --> 00:18:07,400
It's hard to investigate.

256
00:18:08,880 --> 00:18:09,960
Chief.

257
00:18:09,960 --> 00:18:11,400
They aren't unconnected.

258
00:18:12,480 --> 00:18:14,720
People like Ai Xia and Cheng Hui

259
00:18:14,720 --> 00:18:16,560
wrap themselves in kindness,

260
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:18,280
but do shady things in secret.

261
00:18:18,520 --> 00:18:19,720
That counts as a connection.

262
00:18:20,960 --> 00:18:22,760
I read the comments on Shen Man's video.

263
00:18:23,520 --> 00:18:24,840
Many netizens think

264
00:18:24,840 --> 00:18:26,600
the killer is an agent of justice.

265
00:18:31,360 --> 00:18:32,280
Shen Man.

266
00:18:33,480 --> 00:18:35,520
Our video is trending like crazy.

267
00:18:35,520 --> 00:18:36,560
Several brands have already

268
00:18:36,560 --> 00:18:37,640
contacted our studio for endorsements.

269
00:18:38,560 --> 00:18:39,560
That's great.

270
00:18:41,280 --> 00:18:42,080
Turn them all down.

271
00:18:42,080 --> 00:18:43,000
Turn them all down?

272
00:18:43,560 --> 00:18:45,280
A new guesthouse opened by the Divine Tree.

273
00:18:45,280 --> 00:18:46,560
They're offering a really high price.

274
00:18:47,760 --> 00:18:48,760
The Divine Tree...

275
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:51,640
Number 85 was abused by her husband.

276
00:18:52,320 --> 00:18:53,800
Isn't that a bit too coincidental?

277
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:56,640
Could it be related to Cheng Hui's case?

278
00:18:58,040 --> 00:18:59,120
Help me find

279
00:18:59,120 --> 00:19:00,760
all videos related to the Divine Tree.

280
00:19:01,080 --> 00:19:01,640
Hurry up.

281
00:19:02,040 --> 00:19:02,600
Okay.
